OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start to Monday
OL,6,Fwith an isolated shower possible over
OL,7,Fthe hills. Cloud breaking up into the
OL,8,Fafternoon with sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. Generally light westerly
OL,10,Fwinds throughout and feeling pleasant
OL,11,Fin the sunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FLight winds and sunny spells
OL,14,Fto end the day. However, cloud will
OL,15,Fincrease from the west overnight, with
OL,16,Fa little light rain possible on
OL,17,Fwestern hills. A slightly milder night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
