OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA rather cloudy start with a
OL,6,Flittle light rain in the west. Cloud
OL,7,Fthen tending to break up allowing
OL,8,Fshowers to develop, these heavy at
OL,9,Ftimes, especially in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Fmostly dry, settled spell of weather
OL,13,Fwith bright or sunny spells. A spell
OL,14,Fof rain likely into Thursday.
OL,15,FTemperatures near average, but slowly
OL,16,Fedging up.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
